                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>« <a href="/news-05-2016">May 2016</a> | <span style="text-decoration: underline;">June 2016</span> | <a href="/news-07-08-2016">July/August 2016</a> »</strong></p>
</div>
<p>Welcome to this installment of site news, where you discover a cave and enter it, on the search for unknown treasures. All you need is one last haul of treasure to secure your family another night in the cold, upcoming winter, no matter how dangerous the search for it may be.</p>
<p>This is a series showing off news from the site, articles from the past month, and fan-content for you to check out and discover! Be sure to leave a comment with your thoughts!</p>
<h3 id="toc0"><span>On-Site News</span></h3>
<h4 id="toc1"><span>Featured Articles</span></h4>
<ul>
<li>The featured articles for this month are <a href="/scp-2814">SCP-2814</a> (&quot;Heretic of the Torch&quot;) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/anborough" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1568690); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1568690&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="Anborough" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1568690)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/anborough" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1568690); return false;">Anborough</a></span> and <a href="/wanderer-symbols">Wanderer Symbols</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/toadking07" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1632267); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1632267&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="toadking07" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1632267)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/toadking07" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1632267); return false;">toadking07</a></span>. One's about a mask that gives its wielder the power of a false god, and the other is about secret symbols used by the Wanderer's Library. Check them out!</li>
<li>The featured articles from last month were <a href="/scp-2127">SCP-2127</a> (&quot;Hinterkai-fun!&quot;) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fastandbulbous" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2139686); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2139686&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="fastandbulbous" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2139686)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fastandbulbous" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2139686); return false;">fastandbulbous</a></span> and <a href="/footsteps">Footsteps</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/anborough" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1568690); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1568690&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="Anborough" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1568690)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/anborough" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1568690); return false;">Anborough</a></span>. One's about a murder mystery placed on a grave for passerby to solve, and the other is about a son lashing out to his dad for following in his path. Check them out!</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc2"><span>Event-Featured Articles</span></h4>
<ul>
<li>June 1st was International Children's Day! Children are the driving force for our future, and their creativity and worth should be celebrated. <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1553042); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1553042&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="PeppersGhost" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1553042)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1553042); return false;">PeppersGhost</a></span> gave us an answer; have them come up with horrifying abominations. <a href="/scp-1293">Squeedle Deedle Dee!</a></li>
<li>June 19th was Father's Day! A time to celebrate with your father, or if you don't have one/estranged from one, anyone who's a suitable fatherly figure to you. (I hear Wal-Mart sells dads now for free over the holidays.) <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dierubikdie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1527745); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1527745&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="dierubikdie" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1527745)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dierubikdie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1527745); return false;">dierubikdie</a></span> came up with a solution; the <a href="/scp-2053">Paternal Rubik's Cube</a>, a dad who trapped himself inside a Rubik's Cube to be closer to his puzzle-loving son. Oof.</li>
<li>June 30th was Meteor Watch Day! A great occasion to sit outside and watch the stars, hoping to spot a passing meteor burn in the atmosphere. But if you spot a particularly nasty one, one that looks adorned with a sense of elegance, well, you're screwed. But you can also thank <a href="/a-fancy-dinosaur">A Fancy Dinosaur</a> for ordering it courtesy of <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twistedgears" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735681); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735681&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="TwistedGears" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735681)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twistedgears" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735681); return false;">TwistedGears</a></span>.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc3"><span>Rest of the News</span></h4>
<ul>
<li>In the time since the last post and now, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mistbourne" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1665706); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1665706&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="Mistbourne" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1665706)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mistbourne" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1665706); return false;">Mistbourne</a></span> has stepped up from Junior Staff to Operational. Give him a warm welcome :)</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<p>Missing out on articles? Enjoy a recap on the articles from the past month. Be sure to leave a rose for every fallen shark. I hope you enjoy!</p>
<h3 id="toc4"><span>Week of June 1st</span></h3>
<p>Let's play a song for you.</p>
<h4 id="toc5"><span>SCPs</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-2258">SCP-2258</a> (&quot;Stradivarian Instrument Cases&quot;) - Will craftsmanship - nay, artistry - be able to mend the rift between father and son? Played by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/omnisomniac" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2754409); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2754409&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="OmniSomniac" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2754409)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/omnisomniac" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2754409); return false;">OmniSomniac</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-2405">SCP-2405</a> (&quot;2017_acf_nats_fianls.mp4&quot;) - Because quizbowl just isn't hard enough when the questions are only coming from <em>our</em> timeline. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/univine" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(276792); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=276792&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="Univine" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=276792)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/univine" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(276792); return false;">Univine</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-2787">SCP-2787</a> (&quot;A Bridge in ████████&quot;) - CAD software tools are great, but designs are useless if they can't be implemented in the real world. Designed by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/helsen-smith" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2646520); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2646520&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="Helsen Smith" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2646520)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/helsen-smith" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2646520); return false;">Helsen Smith</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-2711">SCP-2711</a> (&quot;<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">定海神针</span> 如意金箍棒&quot;) - Hundreds of years ago, the king of the Xia prevented a great flood. Many years later, the Monkey King would return to finish the job. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1621343&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="SunnyClockwork" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1621343)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;">SunnyClockwork</a></span>.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc6"><span>Tales</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="/on-mount-golgotha-hub">On Mount Golgotha - Hub</a> - <a href="/scp-012">SCP-012</a> holds many mysteries. And its power is creeping into the modern day, with the blood spilled lying on the Foundation to untangle. Arranged by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2000367); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2000367&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="WrongJohnSilver" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2000367)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2000367); return false;">WrongJohnSilver</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/hand-to-hand-combat">Legerdemain</a> - <em>♪On a gathering storm comes a tall handsome man♪ / ♪With a dusty black coat with a Red Right Hand♪</em>. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/d-mos" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1380646); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1380646&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="D-Mos" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1380646)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/d-mos" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1380646); return false;">D-Mos</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/our-mutual-guide">Our Mutual Guide</a> - Power. SCP-012 has it. Power drawn from countless victims, from an ocean of blood. There are those who want to unleash that power. Who want to bring history to a shattering crescendo, and stop time itself. They must travel a dangerous path, from Golgotha to Alagadda. But now they have a guide. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2156983&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="psul" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2156983)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;">psul</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/snail-tale">Snail Tale</a> - Is there anything on this Earth greater than the love of a father for his children? Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pig-catapult" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(233556); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=233556&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="Pig_catapult" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=233556)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pig-catapult" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(233556); return false;">Pig_catapult</a></span>.</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="toc7"><span>Week of June 8th</span></h3>
<p>You shake my reality and you rattle my brain&#8230;</p>
<h4 id="toc8"><span>SCPs</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-2749">SCP-2749</a> (&quot;It's Just Business&quot;) - Mr. Business tells us that business is the path to enlightenment and it should be spread throughout these pagan lands. Business-wise, this all seems like appropriate business. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fingo7" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2273279); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2273279&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="Fingo7" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2273279)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fingo7" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2273279); return false;">Fingo7</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-392">SCP-392</a> (&quot;A Plant Now Found in Site-103, and Formerly Found in the Households of Nobility&quot;) - This rare fruit was created by Daevite thaumaturgy, and passed down through the imperial dynasties of Asia. Supposedly, it possesses magical abilities, created when its owner's head was turned into the original tree. Cultivated by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrwrong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2039383); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2039383&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="MrWrong" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2039383)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrwrong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2039383); return false;">MrWrong</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-2971">SCP-2971</a> (&quot;Whole Lotta (Reality) Shakin' Goin' On!&quot;) - That was a great show! You remember it, don't you? We both went to it, at the Vic Stanley Country Club. Surely you remember… Think about it… Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/multiscoop" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1667582); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1667582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="Multiscoop" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1667582)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/multiscoop" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1667582); return false;">Multiscoop</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-2950-j">SCP-2950-J</a> (&quot;THE POSTCARD&quot;) - <em>WARNING WARNING WARNING. ATTEMPTING TO IMPERSONATE A MEMBER OF THE O5 COUNCIL IS PUNISHABLE BY TERMINATION, SUPER TERMINATION, AND/OR NECROTIZING FUCKTROCUTION</em>. Originally written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/observerseptember" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1488791); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1488791&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="ObserverSeptember" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1488791)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/observerseptember" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1488791); return false;">ObserverSeptember</a></span>, rewritten by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/daveyoufool" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2034230); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2034230&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="daveyoufool" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2034230)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/daveyoufool" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2034230); return false;">daveyoufool</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/scp-2408">SCP-2408</a> (&quot;Orok's Fall&quot;) - Deep beneath the catacombs of Moscow, Klavigar Orok patiently awaits his rebirth. The Russian Mafia has other plans. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/metaphysician" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1698079); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1698079&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="Metaphysician" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1698079)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/metaphysician" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1698079); return false;">Metaphysician</a></span>.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="toc9"><span>Tales</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="/new-job">New Job</a> - Be careful with that little cutey-wutey!! The fate of all mankind may depend on it. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1956625); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1956625&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="DrChandra" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1956625)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1956625); return false;">DrChandra</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/old-kansas-sector-part-11">Old Kansas Sector ~ 11: Intermission</a> - <em><strong>Presidential Debate</strong>. Four Years under Ronald Reagan, or Scarlet King?</em> Channel flipping by <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/mayreder-personnel-file">Faminepulse</a>.</li>
<li><a href="/the-rotting-man-of-stalingrad">Pain</a> - An eldritch terror reminisces about a war more terrible than even it. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/observerseptember" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1488791); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1488791&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="ObserverSeptember" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1488791)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/observerseptember" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1488791); return false;">ObserverSeptember</a></span>.</li>
<li><a href="/primae-formae">Prelude: Primae Formae</a> - Rome burns as an unholy power commands its puppet to perform for all unwilling. Written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869510" alt="Decibelles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;">Decibelles</a></span>.</li>
